===Employers set limits for their employees phones===

A password controlled application to run on the host/charging PC used to set some or all of the following restrictions on the phone

* Control the numbers and or duration of calls that can be made
* Prevent phone from being used at certain times
* Regularly send via SMS the GPS (requires GPS device) location of the phone durring working hours e.g. delivery driver route monitoring
* Record GPS track log whenever it is in range of a certain bluetooth device (the employees company vehicle)
* Record number called, time and duration of calls placed during working hours.
* Disallow installation of non-company-approved software.
